OL,3,CWales braced for third heatwave of the
OL,4,Cyear
OL,6,FTemperatures across Wales are set to
OL,7,Fsoar over the next week, and could
OL,8,Fclimb into the mid 30s in some areas.
OL,10,FEastern parts of the country are
OL,11,Fexpected to reach higher temperatures
OL,12,Fand could enter amber warning
OL,13,Fterritory.
OL,15,FThis is the third heatwave of the
OL,16,Fyear, and while it isn't predicted to
OL,17,Fbe as hot as the last, it is
OL,18,Fanticipated to carry on for longer
OL,19,Fthan the previous heatwaves.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
