OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783874992
OL,3,CWales braced for third heatwave of the
OL,4,Cyear
OL,6,FHumidity is expected to be lower
OL,7,Fhowever, with cooler nights bringing
OL,8,Fsome relief.
OL,10,FThe deputy chief forecaster at the Met
OL,11,FOffice, Steven Keates said people
OL,12,Fshould "take the usual precautions
OL,13,Fwith the heat and the sun".
OL,15,FHe added: "Parts of the UK are
OL,16,Fentering heatwave conditions: the
OL,17,Fthird heatwave in the UK so far this
OL,18,Fyear.
