OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1783874992
OL,3,CWales braced for third heatwave of the
OL,4,Cyear
OL,6,F"However, unlike the May and June
OL,7,Fheatwaves, we are not expecting this
OL,8,Fheatwave to be record-breaking".
OL,10,FSignificant impacts are likely across
OL,11,Fhealth and social care services due to
OL,12,Fthe high temperatures, including a
OL,13,Frise in deaths, particularly among
OL,14,Fthose aged 65 and over or with health
OL,15,Fconditions.
OL,17,FUV and pollen levels are also
OL,18,Fanticipated to be incredibly high.
